videos.description: After the Irish force the turnover, Austin Torres saves the ball from going out of bounds to set up Rex Pflueger layup on the other end.
videos.headline: Great save leads to Notre Dame layup

videos.description: Rex Pflueger intercepts the pass but comes up short on the open layup attempt.
videos.headline: Notre Dame's Pflueger gets steal but misses easy layup

videos.description: Bonzie Colson gets ejected after hitting Glenn Sanabria up high with an elbow and the referees assess a flagrant foul 2.
videos.headline: Notre Dame's Colson ejected for flagrant 2
